      "rationale": "The solver was verified against the ASME V&V 20 pipe-flow benchmark and the FDA nozzle benchmark. Order-of-accuracy testing confirms second-order spatial convergence for momentum and scalar transport equations. Gradation 2 satisfied."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Discretization error",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
