      "acceptanceCriteria": "Grid convergence index (GCI) for hemolysis index QoI must be below 10% at Gradation 2.",
      "rationale": "Three systematically refined meshes (3.2 M, 7.8 M, 18.6 M cells) were evaluated. GCI for the normalized index of hemolysis is 6.1%, below the 10% threshold. The medium mesh (7.8 M) is selected for production runs. Gradation 2 achieved."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
