      "rationale": "Validation experiments cover flow rates of 2.5–6.0 L/min and rotational speeds of 2000–3500 RPM, encompassing the intended CPB operating envelope. Fluid analog (glycerin-saline) viscosity is matched to blood at 37°C. Relevance to CPB use is confirmed. Gradation 2 achieved."
