      "rationale": "The SST k-ω turbulence model and the Giersiepen-Wurzinger hemolysis power-law are standard choices for CFD hemolysis prediction, supported by published literature. Model-form uncertainty is acknowledged qualitatively. Formal model-form error quantification not required at MRL 2; Gradation 1 accepted."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Model inputs",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 1,
