      "acceptanceCriteria": "At MRL 2, Gradation 1 documentation of input parameter sources and nominal values is sufficient.",
      "rationale": "All model input parameters (fluid density, viscosity, hemolysis model constants) are sourced from peer-reviewed literature and documented in the simulation report. Sensitivity analysis is not required at MRL 2; Gradation 1 accepted."
    },
