      "acceptanceCriteria": "At MRL 2, Gradation 1 acknowledgment of test sample characteristics is sufficient.",
      "rationale": "FDA benchmark experiments used bovine blood with documented hematocrit (35±2%) and controlled storage conditions. Sample-to-sample variability is acknowledged as a source of experimental uncertainty. Formal test-sample characterization study not required at MRL 2; Gradation 1 accepted."
    },
