      "acceptanceCriteria": "At MRL 2, Gradation 1 qualitative assessment of parameter equivalency between validation and COU conditions is sufficient.",
      "rationale": "Validation experiments used a glycerin-saline analog fluid; clinical use involves human blood. Viscosity matching at 37°C is confirmed. Differences in non-Newtonian behavior and red blood cell deformability are acknowledged qualitatively. Formal equivalency quantification not required at MRL 2; Gradation 1 accepted."
